OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FYoung people sue 32        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcountries over climate     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fchange                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "What I felt was fear," says Claudia   
OL,6, Duarte Agostinho as she remembers the  
OL,7, extreme heatwave and fires that ripped 
OL,8, through Portugal in 2017 and killed    
OL,9, more than 100 people. "The wildfires   
OL,10, made me really anxious about what sort 
OL,11, of future I would have."               
OL,13,FClaudia, 24, her brother Martim, 20,   
OL,14,Fand her sister Mariana, 11, are among  
OL,15,Fsix young Portuguese people who have   
OL,16,Ffiled a lawsuit against 32 governments,
OL,17,Fincluding all EU member states, the UK,
OL,18,FNorway, Russia, Switzerland and Turkey.
